pytest-dbfixtures
=================

.. image:: https://travis-ci.org/ClearcodeHQ/pytest-dbfixtures.png?branch=master&cache_buster=0.5.2
    :target: https://travis-ci.org/ClearcodeHQ/pytest-dbfixtures
